<i>noun</i>: 역풍 [역풍] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>역풍 [역풍]</dt><br>
<dd>1. headwind; adverse wind</dd><br>
<dd>배가 가는 반대쪽으로 부는 바람.</dd><br>
<dd>The wind blowing directly against the course of a ship.</dd><br>
<dd>2. headwind; backlash</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 일이 뜻한 바와 달리 순조롭게 이루어지지 않고 어려움을 겪음.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A state in which things do not go smoothly and one faces difficulties against one's intention.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>